xfce4-xkb-plugin|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
xfce4-xkb-plugin: xfce4-xkb-plugin (XKB layout switcher for the Xfce panel)
xfce4-xkb-plugin:
xfce4-xkb-plugin: Xfce XKB layout switch plugin for the Xfce panel. It displays the
xfce4-xkb-plugin: current keyboard layout, and refreshes when layout changes. The layout
xfce4-xkb-plugin: can be switched by simply clicking on the plugin. For now the keyboard
xfce4-xkb-plugin: layouts cannot be configured from the plugin itself, they should be
xfce4-xkb-plugin: set in the XF86Config file or some other way (e.g. setxkbmap).
xfce4-xkb-plugin:
xfce4-xkb-plugin: http://goodies.xfce.org/projects/panel-plugins/xfce4-xkb-plugin
xfce4-xkb-plugin:
xfce4-xkb-plugin: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
